The fork includes:
- Agent persona system (self-awareness layer inspired by claude-recall)
- Bootstrap interview system (adapted from claude-recall's 3-round flow)
- Session recovery with active task tracking
- Memory layering with global/project scope
- Memory promotion across projects
- Session archiving with temporal and topic recall
